<!-- Header Sliders 
====================================-->
<div id="tf-sliders">
  <div class="container"><!-- Container -->
    <div id="header-slider" class="carousel slide layout-two" data-ride="carousel">

      <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
      <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item">
          <%= image_tag("paris.jpg") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default tf-btn">Coming Soon</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item active">
          <%= image_tag("lipstick-girl.jpeg") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <a href="/cosmetics" class="btn btn-default tf-btn">Browse Cosmetics</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <%= image_tag("resized-villa.jpeg") %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-default tf-btn">Coming Soon</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row nomargin">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <div class="col-md-4 nopadding">
            <div class="thumb-block c1 active" data-target="#header-slider" data-slide-to="0" >
              <h5>City Reviews</h5>
              <hr>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4 nopadding">
            <div class="thumb-block c2" data-target="#header-slider" data-slide-to="1">
              <h5>Luxury Eco-Friendly Cosmetics</h5>
              <hr>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4 nopadding">
            <div class="thumb-block c3" data-target="#header-slider" data-slide-to="2">
              <h5>Lifestyle</h5>
              <hr>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- End Container -->
</div>


<div id="vlamorous-content">
  <div class="container"><!-- Container -->
    <div class="row"><!-- Row -->
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"> <!-- Left Content for Blog Posts -->
        <div class="post-block"> <!-- Post #1-->
          <h3 class="media-heading">
            Be Vlamorous
          </h3>
          <div class="post-detail text-center">
            <p>Conscioux stands for honest reviews about honest products. Only high-end organic products
            that do not use animal ingredients and animal testing are listed. We help you make 
            responsible choices without compromising on luxury.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-col-md-10 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
              <%= link_to 'Read More About Our Mission', about_path, class: 'btn btn-default btn-block tf-btn color' %>
            </div>
          </div>


        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Blog Body 
====================================-->
<div id="tf-content">
  <div class="container"><!-- Container -->
    <div class="row"><!-- Row -->
      <div class="col-md-8"> <!-- Left Content for Blog Posts -->
        <div class="post-block"> <!-- Post #1-->
          <div class="post-detail">
            <a href="archives.html" class="meta-date"><span class="bolder">23</span><br>April</a>
              <h2><a href="single-blog.html">Become The Best Fashion Designer</a></h2> <!-- Post Title-->

              <div class="img-wrap"> <!-- Image Wrap -->
                <div class="metas">
                  <a href="fashion.html" class="meta-cat">Fashion</a>
                  <a href="authors.html" class="meta-author">Conscioux</a>
                </div>
                <img src="http://placehold.it/800x450" class="img-responsive" alt="image">
              </div>

              <p>You know you're destined to be a fashion designer if you: a) spent most of your childhood making clothes for your Barbie dolls instead of playing with your friends; b) read fashion magazines instead of your school books; c) ran a boutique out of your basement at age 10. In other words: if you want to be the next Yves Saint Laurent, it helps to be completely and utterly obsessed with fashion.</p>
              <p>However, there are many aspects of the profession. Working as a fashion designer can just as well mean supervising a design team at a sportswear company as producing a label under your own name. Although the former career may not seem as glamorous as the latter, it certainly will make your life less stressful. To create your own label takes a lot of time, dedication and hard work. Not to mention living just above the poverty line for several years[...]</p>
            </div>

            <a href="single-blog.html" class="btn btn-default tf-btn txt-link">Continue Reading</a>
          </div><!-- end Post #1-->


              
              
          </div><!-- End of Posts/Blogrol -->


          <div class="col-md-4"> <!-- Right content for sidebar and widget area-->
            <div class="sidebar"><!-- sidebar -->
              <div class="widget search"><!-- Search Widget -->
                <div class="widget-wrap">
                  <%= form_tag(search_pages_path, role: "search") do %>
                  <div class="input-group">
                    <%= text_field_tag :search_cosmetics, nil, placeholder: "Search Reviews", class: "form-control" %>
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                    <%= submit_tag "Search", class: "btn btn-default" %>
                    </span>
                  <% end %>
                  </div><!-- /input-group -->
                </div>
              </div>
  
              <div class="widget recent"><!-- Recent Post Widget -->
                <h4>Recent Reviews</h4>
                <div class="widget-wrap">
                  <% @cosmetics_reviews.each do |review| %>
                    <div class="thumb-post"><!-- Thumbnail Post #1 -->
                      <%= link_to review do %>
                        <div class="info">
                          <h3 class="media-heading"><%= review.cosmetics_review_title %></h3>
                           <%= image_tag(review.image, class: "img-responsive") %>
                        </div>
                      <% end %>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            
        </div><!-- end sidebar -->
      </div><!-- end Right content for sidebar and widget area-->
    </div><!-- end Row -->
  </div><!-- End Container -->
</div>


    